text: Mael Kaudre is a footballer who played attack for the New Caledonia national football team. He scored a goal against the Fiji national football team in Ba, Fiji during the Oceania world cup qualifier. He also played in the 2008 OFC Nations Cup. He played attack for Noumea-based A.S. Magenta, in the New Caledonia Division Honneur league, from 2006 through 2009. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:New Caledonian footballers Category:AS Magenta players Category:Association footballers not categorized by position
